ser ，所以唔係好想睇返呢d牌子<br />\n其實bba唔係唔好，但好似周街都係。5系中港車附近都已經好多。audi揸左好內又想換下牌子，如果考慮都應該只會諗e class 或者benz嘅suv<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 70萬呢個budget唔高又唔低，好難諗，好想要部300匹以上嘅車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2手會唔會多dd選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 前幾日去左九龍灣睇，但都只係睇左s7，macan s, ghibli, discovery<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日諗到我就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d30f4f8879e5855cb486f6f5e2fa09b97c3638d","tid":350521,"uid":114166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買兩部<br />\n一部買新<br />\n一部買二手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17a5c9a8b6b751f66445f9b20f2f293bf822362","tid":350521,"uid":73,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:00:27.000Z","msg":"明你想要乜<br />\n本來叫你出520d, <br />\n但你應該追求馬力多過油錢<br />\n<br />\n700k 買e class 冇乜option, 力水達唔到你要求<br />\n你要快, 操控, sedan<br />\nbudget 升到800k<br />\n買全新rs3 sedan<br />\n新底盤, 新2.5 turbo, 新鋁合金車架, under1500kg, 400匹<br />\n0-100km 外國review 實測3.7s<br />\n山路直路玩晒"},{"pid":"b67f053972bbe265f5a186f7615fed2cf90248b9","tid":350521,"uid":12523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:08:24.000Z","msg":"m2"},{"pid":"79c825a5393caefcb93d60e5f9516d7fc9c8d266","tid":350521,"uid":114166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明你想要乜<br />\n本來叫你出520d, <br />\n但你應該追求馬力多過油錢<br />\n<br />\n700k 買e class 冇乜option, 力水達唔到你要求<br />\n你要快, 操控, sedan<br />\nbudget 升到800k<br />\n買全新rs3 sedan<br />\n新底盤, 新2.5 turbo, 新鋁合金車架, under1500kg, 400匹<br />\n0-100km 外國review 實測3.7s<br />\n山路直路玩晒</blockquote><blockquote>引用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果買到rs3就正啦，但我屋企人應該會覺得後座leg room 會唔夠，太細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實macan後座都唔係好多leg room，可能SUV大架d，佢地可能覺得後座會鬆動d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a96308a05945bd0ddd0987093235853c061b022","tid":350521,"uid":114166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>m2</blockquote><br />\n肯定冇可能2門，我都好想要m2，但唔實際，始終有時要返大陸，有時要車下貨，車多1，2個人咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba08f4383a98acaad2d8bd2f84bac526e3aeb52","tid":350521,"uid":59046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>m2</blockquote><br />\n肯定冇可能2門，我都好想要m2，但唔實際，始終有時要返大陸，有時要車下貨，車多1，2個人咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2手 M6 gran coupe"},{"pid":"2ea2c2bfa19cbf0097b04669a54e0809518bc897","tid":350521,"uid":84472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T19:54:59.000Z","msg":"你咁多車 買多架咩車有乜所謂"},{"pid":"e71d50cafb1b35f946649b0e8842437b89207ff4","tid":350521,"uid":133480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T02:34:57.000Z","msg":"F pace啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73c8a1e260037d237e1d7686c90573ef826ed31","tid":350521,"uid":114166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T21:12:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>m2</blockquote><br />\n肯定冇可能2門，我都好想要m2，但唔實際，始終有時要返大陸，有時要車下貨，車多1，2個人咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2手 M6 gran coupe</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n70萬budget 有買到咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca7e0c384f99e6a45ae5fa22280292a72dd767d","tid":350521,"uid":114166,